    \SYS_Random_34 \sysFn= 34! Pos=
    Pos<,      128- [if<0 157+] 1+   {1..157}   $fe& Pos<.
    Pos>, 127& 64-  [if<0 109+] $11+ {$11..$fd} $fe& Pos>.
    Pos, 4^ if<>0loop]
  DrawBlock!
  pop ret
] AddFood=

